reviewText: I bought this video for my two nieces and they won't stop playing it!  The music is great and best of all, I like it too.  Would love to see a series of these videos.
This is a fabulous video!  The music is OUTSTANDING!  My children are loving it!  I highly recommend this for ANYONE with kids under age 6!

This video has it all- and it doesn't drive me crazy-the companion cassette makes it a great thing to have in the car-but it is a sleeper and hard to find-i have talked to the girls who made this video-they have won every award under the sun-the critics and kids love it but there needs to  be a grassroots campaign to get it going-Rosie O'Donnel-Oprah WHERE ARE  YOU?
